                  throws edu.ma02.core.exceptions.CityException,

                         edu.ma02.core.exceptions.SensorException
        Adds a new sensor to a station
        Specified by:
        addSensor in interface edu.ma02.core.interfaces.ICity
        Parameters:
        string - sensor id
        string1 - station name (used to identify the station) in which the sensor will be added
        icc - cartesian coordinates in which the sensor is installed
        igc - geographic coordinates in which the sensor is installed
        Returns:
        1.true if the sensor was inserted in the collection storing all sensors

        2.false if the sensor already exists

        Throws:
        edu.ma02.core.exceptions.CityException - if the station doesn't exists or if param stationName parameter is null
        edu.ma02.core.exceptions.StationException - uncatched from station if the sensor doesn't exists or the sensorId is invalid (i.e. less or more than 10 characters)
        edu.ma02.core.exceptions.SensorException - uncatched from sensor if the sensorId is invalid (i.e. less or more than 10 characters)

                       throws edu.ma02.core.exceptions.CityException,

                              edu.ma02.core.exceptions.SensorException,
                              edu.ma02.core.exceptions.MeasurementException
        Adds a new measurement to a sensor from a station
        Specified by:
        addMeasurement in interface edu.ma02.core.interfaces.ICity
        Parameters:
        string - station name used to identify the station
        string1 - sensor id in which the measurement will be associated
        d - measurement value
        string2 - measurement unit for which the value was recorded
        ldt - measurement date for which the value was recorded
        Returns:
        1.true if the measurement was inserted in the collection storing all sensors

        2.false if the measurement already exists

        Throws:
        edu.ma02.core.exceptions.CityException - if the station doesn't exists or if @param string parameter is null
        edu.ma02.core.exceptions.StationException - uncatched from station if the sensor doesn't exists
        edu.ma02.core.exceptions.SensorException - uncatched from sensor if the unit is not compatible with the unit pre-defined for the sensor
        edu.ma02.core.exceptions.MeasurementException - uncatched from measurement if the value is -99 or any parameter is invalid
